{"tid":1546122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔夠膽跳閘嘅入一入嚟，畀少少提示你","createTime":"2019-09-06T07:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T11:55:09.000Z","uid":146535,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"498538f2b8e818cdf35006cd44a7b8909bd6d6d3","tid":1546122,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:11:27.000Z","msg":"起碼葵芳、太子、元朗、九龍灣跳啦好唔好<br />\n呢幾單野真係離撚晒譜<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">葵芳咁樣放催淚彈根本當香港人唔係人係豬<br />\n811<br />\n葵芳催淚彈 唔譴責黑警 事後仲要我地自己清潔</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HAJBrfw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHAJBrfw.jpg&h=6865df8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831<br />\n太子黑警無差別打人 警鐵合作 仲嚴重過721</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfJUXnd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfJUXnd.jpg&h=35b6ff54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n元朗唔洗講啦下話<br />\n九龍灣黨鐵總站<br />\n你出閘我唔理你啦，你咪講個最近嘅站補飛咪算<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔跳真係被人睇死，咁多單野呢幾單最多人知都係最嬲<br />\n我起碼呢4 個站一定跳"},{"pid":"3f13d19d23c9f34b4497193e478fe32aacc4c4b2","tid":1546122,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08a6a75887750d6a4fbdf14ae1324c58fdd5727d","tid":1546122,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=35339699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"